From the original set of half a million products, we  compute a success rate s for the 48,218 products that had at least one purchase made through a recommendation and for which a price was given.
We use a regression of the following product attributes to correlate them with recommendation success : • r : number of recommendations • ns : number of senders of recommendations • nr : number of recipients of recommendations • p : price of the product • v : number of reviews of the product • t : average product rating 235 category np n 